<gtm desc="This example shows the use of 'PipePort' components to model fuel puddling and evaporation in the intake ports, demonstrates the use of 'EngCylTWallSoln' to calculate cylinder wall temperatures, and predicts burn rate by modeling in-cylinder flame propagation using 'EngCylCombSITurb'. " force_doe="false" original_ver="6.2.0" product="1" restart_mode="NORMAL" ver="2016.2.8721">
